Tables are provided by the Resource Assessment and Conservation Engineering Division (RACE) Shellfish Assessment Program (SAP) of the Alaska Fisheries Science Center (AFSC).There are legal restrictions on access to the data. These data are not intended for public dissemination and should not be shared without the explicit written consent of the data managers and owners (NOAA Fisheries).The GitHub repository for the scripts that created this code can be found at (https://github.com/EmilyMarkowitz-NOAA/sap_products).
